name: Mew Mew Nitro
description:
Turbo cat loves Christmas and wants to sneak a peek at her gift. She has to make it over the obstacles put in her way to get that sneak peek at her Christmas gift. Race over the obstacles to reach it as fast as you can but be careful not to let your paws get too hot!

Use Left/Right Arrow Keys to Move and Space to Jump. Good luck!

This game is available open-source at https://github.com/instafluff/MewMewNitro
